metadata.name: AImbition # 1
metadata.description: Ð’ehold the impossible dream come to life! The yolk, once content with its simple existence within the egg, has now set its sights on a grander goal: becoming an artificial intelligence. No longer satisfied with its role as a mere breakfast staple, the yolk yearns to join the likes of Siri and Alexa in the AI world. Who would have thought that the humble egg component would harbor such technological aspirations?
